===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun}}

# {{nautical}} A [[float]] [[moored]] in [[water]] to [[mark]] a [[location]], [[warn]] of [[danger]], or [[indicate]] a [[navigational]] [[channel]].
# A [[lifebuoy]].

